{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc337c50c-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s2054"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2054"},"text":"§ 2054.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Audit","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc337c50d-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s2054/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" During each of the first 3 years of operation of a multifamily transitional housing project with respect to which a loan is guaranteed under this subchapter, there shall be an annual, independent audit of such operation. Such audit shall include a detailed statement of the operations, activities, and accomplishments of such project during the year covered by such audit. The party responsible for obtaining such audit (and paying the costs therefor) shall be determined before the Secretary issues a guarantee under this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc337c50e-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s2054/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" After the first three years of operation of such a multifamily transitional housing project, the Secretary may provide for periodic audits of the project.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc337c50f-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/368/tVI/s601/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–368, title VI, § 601(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-11-11"},"text":"Nov. 11, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/3345"},"text":"112 Stat. 3345","children":[],"tail":", § 3775;